</div>
<div class="comment" id="comment-47761498">
  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/VerifiedReports">VerifiedReports</a> 1 day ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">Looks more useful than the Cut page.<p>Meanwhile, I wish BMD would take a step back and do the housecleaning that Resolve so desperately needs. They threw a bunch of purchased products together on different pages and called it &quot;integrated,&quot; when in fact the integration is buggy and janky.<p>The #1 thing they need to do is integrate all the nodeviews. A single nodeview for all processing would make Resolve a truly groundbreaking product, and undoubtedly eliminate a lot of bugs.</div>
