  <div class="comment_text">I&#x27;d been trying to migrate from LR to RapidRaw, but it&#x27;s been tough as most features are just trying to catch up to LR. DaVinci handles a lot of things better than LR from the start. Going to give it a go. Crossing my fingers</div>
  
